Megatron turned his attention to Autofire. "Head to these coordinats, 
and take Divebomb" he then turned to the Stunticons, "Transform 
Stunticons, and move out. Triggerhappy, Skullgrin, follow them. 
Somebody get Stratus out here," He then walked towards Cyclonus, "I am 
riding in you" he commanded.


Wildrider and SPeedbreaker quickly transformed and sped off. 
Motormaster turned to Symphony. "You ride with me," he told him, and 
transformed into his truck mode, opening his trailer compartment.
